    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You place this shroud on a target creature, causing ice to form under its feet or on its wings. The target can only walk at half speed, and only by succeeding at a DC 10 Acrobatics check. If the target flies using wings, it can only fly at half speed, and only by succeeding at a DC 10 Fly check. If it fails it cannot move that round and must succeed at a Reflex save or fall. If it fails by 5 or more it immediately falls, with no Reflex save. If the target does not move on its turn, it does not need to attempt this check and is not considered flat-footed for using Acrobatics to move over uneven ground.</p>\n",
